                        <interp inst="t18350615-name-737" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM HEIGHWAY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable N</hi> 232.) I took the prisoner, and found these things in her apron.</p>
               <p>(Ellen Wade gave the prisoner a good character.)</p>
